{
  "stem": "93.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There is little doubt that at that time we could have gone to Berlin and gotten there before the Russians.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But in any event, the politics of the situation where such that we gave up all of the land that we had captured, turned around, and went south.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we went across the-- I think it was the Danube River.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was Donau, which is Danube.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we crossed into Austria at a city called Brunau, B-R-U-N-A-U.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And when we got into Austria, we once again began to run into displaced people who were trying now to get away from the Russians.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the-- these people, I now found out, had as much hatred for the Russians as they did for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because by this time, many of the Russian divisions were-- were manned by Mongolian troops who were incredibly cruel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And there was a great deal of raping and pillaging and all that sort of stuff going on, because the-- the Russian army apparently did not have the same standards at the time as we did, or else they didn't care.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Because the people that they were doing this to were the Germans, whom they, probably with good reason, despised.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
